The Autumn Kernel Project
=========================

* Still naive, still experimental.

This project is a fork of SouthWest kernel. It designed for Redmi Note 7
(lavender) devices.

This branch is included KernelSU by rsuntk[1]. 

If you want to use this kernel, please use a RDP[2] ROM and your 
device's original kernel version is 4.19. If your device's original 
version isn't 4.19, please find a k4.19 ROM and flash it.

This project is experimental forever. Use at your own risk.

Enjoy it :)

[1]: https://github.com/rsuntk/KernelSU
[2]: Retrofit Dynamic Partitions
